# Demo Constraints

## Never do these
- Add Salesforce, Data Cloud, Agentforce, or any backend API integration
- Create real orders, cases, claims, payments, refunds, credits, coupons, or shipments
- Install npm dependencies
- Commit or push without explicit user approval
- Delete files (deprecate/bypass instead)
- Mutate files inside `controller-health-react-handoff/`

## Trigger logic — do not touch
The 5-navigation proactive toast trigger lives in `src/components/Ps5HomeScreen.jsx`.
The rule: `navigationCount >= 5` with `!hasTriggered && !dismissed`.
Do not change this threshold or the keydown/keyup distinct-press logic without explicit approval.

## Assets
- Only import images from `assets/` using Vite static imports.
- Never use numbered reference screenshots (1.png–7.png) as runtime assets.
- Allowed controller images: `ps5-controller.png`, `dualsense-edge.png`, `dualsense-limited-astro-bot.png`

## Validation
After every substantive edit, run `npm run build` and confirm exit code 0.
